Blood Pointer is a groundbreaking platform designed to revolutionize blood donation and recipient mapping. Our mission is simple yet profoundly impactful- connecting donors with individuals urgently in need of blood.

With Blood Pointer, finding a blood donor or recipient is easier and more efficient than ever before. Our user-friendly interface allows donors to register and specify their blood type, availability, and location. Simultaneously, recipients can search for donors based on their specific requirements and reach out in times of need.



